					<p> This blog features news about African agriculture. Its aims are critiquing competing agricultural paradigms, encouraging, motivating African agriculturalists, sharing experiences from outside Africa, contributing to debate on Africa’s food security needs, asking tough questions, expressing strong opinions.</p>
